							</TextBlock>
						</Expander>
						<Expander Header="Special thanks" Margin="0,0,0,10">
							<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap"><Run Text="Special thanks to:"/><LineBreak/>
								Etra for the info regarding the coordinate system.<LineBreak/>
